These are Puzzles for 7x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-3-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, coffee, sprite, tea
There 4 different types of food: apple, cranberry, kale, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, skydiving, reading, collecting
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, manager, paramedic, software-developer
4 different pets are kept: dog, goldfish, pony, mouse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, basketball, cycling, skiing
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, roller, tram
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 2. the person who's sport is cycling is the person eating strawberry##1
 3. the person eating cranberry is on the far left##1
 4. the person who's hobby is reading is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 5. the engineer is on the right of the paramedic##1
 6. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
 7. the manager is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
 9. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
11. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
12. the person drinking juice is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person eating strawberry##2
13. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
14. the person drinking tea is the owner of the pony##1
15. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person eating apple##3
16. the person driving the roller is on the far left or far right##3
17. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Beverage    | tea   | juice            | coffee | sprite        |
| Food        | cranberry       | kale         | strawberry     | apple       |
| Hobby       | skydiving     | sudoku        | collecting     | reading |
| Job         | manager     | software-developer | paramedic    | engineer   |
| Pet         | pony    | mouse         | dog        | goldfish         |
| Sport       | skiing    | water-polo       | cycling    | basketball     |
| Transport   | roller | tram     | motorbike         | airplane         |

