.:: Puzzle 7x4-Level-3-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, soy-milk, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: banana, mango, garlic, pear
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, firefighter, architect, musician
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, western, time-travel, fantasy
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, polish, malaysian, chinese
4 different pets are kept: frog, bird, mouse, chinchilla
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, parkour, cricket, baseball
 1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
 2. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is baseball and the owner of the bird##2
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the italian##1
 4. the person watching action movies is the person eating pear##1
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the owner of the bird is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person eating pear##1
 8. the musician is the person eating garlic##1
 9. the person eating mango is between the malaysian and the person who's sport is cricket##2
10. the software-developer is on the left of the architect##1
11. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
12. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
13. the person drinking soy-milk is the person who's sport is sailing##1
14. the person eating banana is on the far right##1
15. the polish is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
16. the person watching fantasy movies is the italian##1
17. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the software-developer##3

.:: Answer ::.
