There 4 different types of food: kiwi, artichoke, avocado, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, reading, writing, chess
The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, dancer, chef, software-developer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, satire, martial-arts, animation
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog, mouse, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming, water-polo, surfing
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person drinking coffee is the dancer##1
 3. the person eating avocado is the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the person watching crime movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 5. the person eating kiwi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
 6. the mechanic is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
 7. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person who's sport is swimming##3
 9. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
10. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
12. the person drinking fanta is the person who's sport is surfing##1
13. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
14. the person who's hobby is writing is the owner of the mouse##1
15. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
16. the person watching animation movies is the software-developer##1
17. the person watching satire movies is the dancer##1
18. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person eating avocado##1

